118
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,480
My sad drama?

119
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,320
Dou Huaizhong,

120
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,120
Mr. Mayor,

121
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,400
speaking of drama,

122
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,800
