dirty, and stingy.

125
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,200
Qian Tong is unhandsome,

126
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,960
but he's willing to spend money on me.

127
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,400
What about you?

128
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,880
Dou Huaizhong,

129
